value.0: Qixoni crystals are exceedingly rare lightsaber crystals of a dark red color. These unique, powerful gems are formed when a certain planet is consumed as its star went supernova. The power of a Qixoni crystal can only be harnessed by one with great strength in the Dark side of the Force. The crystal is said to enhance one's Force abilities, in addition to enhancing the lightsaber blade's power to significant degree.
